title: Rubio rallies GOP faithful in conservative stronghold Utah
text:
> Florida Rubio rallies GOP faithful in conservative stronghold Utah Republican presidential candidate Sen. Marco Rubio, R-Fla., poses for a photograph with Arleny Dimond during a campaign rally at the Utah State Fairpark Monday, Oct. 19, 2015, in Salt Lake City. Rubio is the fourth presidential candidate to make a stop in Utah in recent months. (AP Photo/Rick Bowmer) iWitness7 is your chance to join the News Center 7 team!
